{"tid":1083272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長洲人形物海面漂浮惹虛驚","createTime":"2019-03-29T13:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T13:41:12.000Z","uid":3090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eb3cb59aec51bf1b3cfe03cdfa9dc8799687c013","tid":1083272,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T13:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LmmwFzE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLmmwFzE.png&h=fc00b889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n救援人員到場搜索。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n長洲發生懷疑墮海事件，傍晚6時許，有市民發現東灣對開50米海面有人形物體漂浮，於是報案。救援人員接報到場，正在現場搜索懷疑墮海人士。至晚上7時許，消防蛙人落水搜索，撿獲一個魚網，相信事件是虛驚一場。"},{"pid":"4e24b9600bccd3b9dc82d747f233cd3c40cffa06","tid":1083272,"uid":233593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T13:39:47.000Z","msg":"諗起柚木巴單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4819d85728bb7dcf6ff104e08004d451efe57740","tid":1083272,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T13:41:12.000Z","msg":"But is it though <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相信已被嫌犯偷龍轉鳳"}]}